chination"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 阴谋(an artful or secret plot or scheme)"},{"type":"text","text":"编子↓"},{"type":"text","text":"[mae{r'nex{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：machin（机械：制造）+ation→阴谋"},{"type":"text","text":"肥线变始"},{"type":"entry","text":"beseech","headword":"beseech"},{"type":"text","text":"悬求"},{"type":"text","text":"[br'si:t]"},{"type":"text","text":"固词根记忆：be（使）+seech（看作seek，寻求）→寻求→恳求"},{"type":"entry","text":"jargon","headword":"jargon"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.胡言乱语(confused language)：行话（the technical"},{"type":"text","text":"['d3a:rgan]"},{"type":"text","text":"terminology)"},{"type":"text","text":"The First World War began in a context of jargon and"},{"type":"text","text":"machination"},{"type":"text","text":"verbal delicacy and continued in a cloud of euphemism"},{"type":"text","text":"as impenetrable as language and literature, skillfully used, could make it."},{"type":"entry","text":"doff","headword":"doff"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.脱掉（外衣、帽子（to take off）"},{"type":"text","text":"[da:f]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：d+off（脱掉）→把衣服脱掉→脱掉（外衣、帽子）"},{"type":"entry","text":"stentorian","headword":"stentorian"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj声音洪亮的（extremely loud)"},{"type":"text","text":"[sten'to:rian]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自希腊神话特洛伊战争中的传令官Stentor，其声音极其洪亮。"},{"type":"entry","text":"expurgate","headword":"expurgate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 删除，删节(to remove passages considered obscene or objectionable)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ekspargert]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：ex（使）+purg（纯洁；变干净）+ate→使变干净→删除"},{"type":"entry","text":"unscrupulous","headword":"unscrupulous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj肆无忌惟的（unprincipled)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'skru:pjalas]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：un(不)+scrupulous(小v心的)→肆无忌惮的"},{"type":"text","text":"The value of Davis’ sociological research is compromised by his unscrupulous"},{"type":"text","text":"tendency to use materials selectively in order to substantiate his own claims,"},{"type":"text","text":"while dlisregarding information that points to other possible conclusions."},{"type":"entry","text":"chancy","headword":"chancy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不确定的，不安的(involving risks and uncertainty)"},{"type":"text","text":"['tfaensi]"},{"type":"entry","text":"accredit","headword":"accredit"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 授权(to give official authorization to or approval of)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'kredrt]"},{"type":"text","text":"accredit sb.to委任、委派"},{"type":"entry","text":"nonthreatening","headword":"nonthreatening"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.不构成威胁的"},{"type":"text","text":"[na:n'θretnin]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：non（不）+threatening（威胁的）→不构成威胁的"},{"type":"entry","text":"irradiate","headword":"irradiate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 照射(to cast rays of light upon); 照羅，照亮(to shine; light up)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ir（使）+radi（光线，辐射）+ate→使有光线→照射；照耀"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'rerdiert]"},{"type":"entry","text":"cardiac","headword":"cardiac"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 心脏的(relating to the heart)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka:rdiaek]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：card（心）+iac（有病的）→心脏的"},{"type":"entry","text":"excise","headword":"excise"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 切除，删去(to remove by cutting out or away)"},{"type":"text","text":"['eksarz]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：ex（向外）+cis（切）+e→切出去→切除"},{"type":"entry","text":"contrition","headword":"contrition"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 悔罪，痛梅(remorse for having done wrong)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'trx[n]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自contrite（adj.痛悔的）"}]},{"number":337,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"buckle","headword":"buckle"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 皮带扣环 v 扣紧(to fasten or join with a buckle)"},{"type":"text","text":"['bAkl]"},{"type":"text","text":"buckleup扣紧安全带"},{"type":"entry","text":"inhibition","headword":"inhibition"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.阻上;抑制(the act of inhibiting);抑制物(sth. that forbids, debars, or restricts)"},{"type":"text","text":"William James lacked the usual awe of death; writing to his dying father, he"},{"type":"text","text":"[inhr'bifn]"},{"type":"text","text":"spoke without inhibition about the old man's impending death."},{"type":"entry","text":"clemency","headword":"clemency"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.温和(mildness,esp.of weather);仁慈，宽厚(mercy)"},{"type":"text","text":"['klemansi]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：和cement（n.水泥）一起记"},{"type":"text","text":"caritas, charity. lenity"},{"type":"entry","text":"disillusion","headword":"disillusion"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使梦想破灭，使醒悟(to cause to lose naive faith and trust)"},{"type":"text","text":"[drsr'lu:3n]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：dis（不）+illusion（幻想）→不再有幻想→使梦想破灭，使醒悟"},{"type":"entry","text":"anticlimactic","headword":"anticlimactic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 奖减的(of, relating to, or marked by anticlimax)"},{"type":"text","text":"[aentiklar'maektrk]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：anti（相反）+climac（看作climax，顶点）+tic→与顶点相反→突减的"},{"type":"entry","text":"undecipherable","headword":"undecipherable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 难破译的(not easily deciphered)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Andr'sarfrabl]"},{"type":"entry","text":"defamation","headword":"defamation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 讲谤，中伤(the act of defaming another)"},{"type":"text","text":"[defa'mexfn]"},{"type":"text","text":"aspersion, calumniation, denigration, vilification"},{"type":"entry","text":"rubbery","headword":"rubbery"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.橡胶似的，有弹性的（resembling rubber as in elasticity, consistency, or"},{"type":"text","text":"['rAbari]"},{"type":"text","text":"texture)"},{"type":"entry","text":"skinflint","headword":"skinflint"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.客画鬼（miser;niggard)"},{"type":"text","text":"['skinflint]"},{"type":"text","text":"园参考词组：skinaflint（爱财如命）"},{"type":"entry","text":"dutiful","headword":"dutiful"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 尽职的(filled with a sense of duty)"},{"type":"text","text":"['du:trfl]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自duty（n.责任）"},{"type":"entry","text":"deviant","headword":"deviant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 越出常规的(deviating especially from an accepted norm)"},{"type":"text","text":"['di:viant]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：de（偏离）+vi(路）+ant→偏离道路→越轨→越出常规的"},{"type":"entry","text":"complacence","headword":"complacence"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 自满(satisfaction with oneself)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kam'plersns]"}]},{"number":338,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 30 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"sobriety","headword":"sobriety"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.节制(moderation)：庄重(gravity)"},{"type":"text","text":"[sa'brarati]"},{"type":"text","text":"The sumptuous costumes of Renaissance Italy, with their gold and silver"},{"type":"text","text":"embroidery and figured brocades, were the antithesis of Spanish sobriety, with"},{"type":"example","text":"its dark muted colors, plain short capes, and high collars edged with small ruffs."},{"type":"entry","text":"obstinacy","headword":"obstinacy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 固执，候强，顽固(the state of being obstinate; stubbornness)"},{"type":"text","text":"['a:bstinasi]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：ob（反）+stin（=stand站）+acy→反着站→固执，倔强"},{"type":"entry","text":"reaffirmation","headword":"reaffirmation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 再肯定(renewed affirmation)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ri:aefar'mexfn]"},{"type":"entry","text":"spiritedness","headword":"spiritedness"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.有精神，活泼"},{"type":"text","text":"['spiritidnas]"},{"type":"text","text":"liveliness, vivaciousness"},{"type":"entry","text":"overbalance","headword":"overbalance"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使失去平衡（to cause to lose balance）"},{"type":"text","text":"[auvar'baelans]"},{"type":"entry","text":"affectionate","headword":"affectionate"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.亲爱的，挚爱的(having affection or warm regard)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'fekfanat]"},{"type":"text","text":"3 He is very affectionate towards his children."},{"type":"entry","text":"sultry","headword":"sultry"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 网热的(very hot and humid; sweltering); (人)风骚的(capable of exciting strong"},{"type":"text","text":"['sAltri]"},{"type":"text","text":"sexual desires)"},{"type":"entry","text":"possessed","headword":"possessed"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 着迷的，入迷的(influenced or controlled by sth.)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pa'zest]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自possess（v拥有：迷住）"},{"type":"entry","text":"dumbbell-like","headword":"dumbbell-like"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj哑铃状的"},{"type":"text","text":"['dambel,lark]"},{"type":"text","text":"图组合词：dumbbell(哑铃）+like（像）→哑铃状的"},{"type":"entry","text":"collusive","headword":"collusive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 共谋的S(having secret agreement or cooperaition)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka'lu:s1v]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：col（共同）+lus（玩）+ive→一起玩→共谋的"},{"type":"entry","text":"molten","headword":"molten"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.熔融的，熔化的(melted)"},{"type":"text","text":"['maultan]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自melt（v融化，熔化）"},{"type":"entry","text":"postoperative","headword":"postoperative"},{"type":"definition","text":"adji. 手术后的(following a surgical operation)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pa:st'a:paratrv]"},{"type":"text","text":"图postoperative care 术后护理"},{"type":"entry","text":"stumble","headword":"stumble"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 继程(to strike one’s foot against sth. and almost fall)"},{"type":"text","text":"['stAmbl]"},{"type":"text","text":"lurch, stagger, trip"},{"type":"entry","text":"contemptible","headword":"contemptible"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj令人轻视的（despicable)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'temptabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自contempt（n.蔑视，轻视）"},{"type":"entry","text":"transferable","headword":"transferable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 可转移的(that can be moved from one place, person or use to another)"},{"type":"text","text":"[trans'f3:rabl]"},{"type":"entry","text":"acquiescent","headword":"acquiescent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 默认的(inclined to acquiesce)"},{"type":"text","text":"[akwi'esnt]"},{"type":"entry","text":"touchy","headword":"touchy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.敏感的，易怒的(acutely sensitive or irritable)"},{"type":"text","text":"['tAtfi]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：touch（触摸）+y→一触即发的→敏感的，易怒的"}]},{"number":339,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"oligarch","headword":"oligarch"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 募头政治 (a member of a form of government in which a small group of people"},{"type":"text","text":"[a:laga:rk]"},{"type":"text","text":"hold all the power); 寡头统治集团(a member of a small governing faction)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：olig（少数）+arch（统治）→由少数人来统治→寡头政治"},{"type":"entry","text":"agoraphobic","headword":"agoraphobic"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.患旷野恐惧症的人ad恐旷症的"},{"type":"text","text":"[aegara'faubrk]"},{"type":"entry","text":"trademark","headword":"trademark"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 特征正 (a dlistinguishing characteristic or feature firmly associated with a person"},{"type":"text","text":"['trerdma:rk]"},{"type":"text","text":"or thing）：商标v.保证商标权（to secure trademarkrights）"},{"type":"entry","text":"cozy","headword":"cozy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 舒适的，惬意的(marked by or providing contentment"},{"type":"text","text":"['kauzi]"},{"type":"text","text":"or comfort)：亲切友好的(friendly)"},{"type":"entry","text":"serial","headword":"serial"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 连续的，—系列的(arranged in a series of things)"},{"type":"text","text":"[srrial]"},{"type":"text","text":"serialkiller连环杀手"},{"type":"text","text":"evergreen"},{"type":"entry","text":"unecological","headword":"unecological"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj非生态的"},{"type":"text","text":"[ani:ka'la:dzrkl]"},{"type":"entry","text":"verified","headword":"verified"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad已查清的，已证实的"},{"type":"text","text":"[verrfard]"},{"type":"definition","text":"A hypothesis must not only account for what we already know, but it must also"},{"type":"text","text":"be venifiec by continued observation."},{"type":"entry","text":"wavy","headword":"wavy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.波状的，多浪的(rising or swelling in waves)：波动起伏的(marked by"},{"type":"text","text":"[wervi]"},{"type":"text","text":"undulation)"},{"type":"entry","text":"fluffy","headword":"fluffy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj有绒毛的（covered with fluff);无聊的，琐碎的（light or frivolous）"},{"type":"text","text":"[fAf]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自fluff(n.绒毛）"},{"type":"entry","text":"hardheaded","headword":"hardheaded"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.（尤指做生意时）讲究实际的，冷静的，精明的（shrewd andunsentimental;"},{"type":"text","text":"[ha:rd'hedid]"},{"type":"text","text":"practical)"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：hard（硬的）+head(头）+ed→头脑坚硬的→冷静的"},{"type":"entry","text":"defiant","headword":"defiant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj反抗的，挑胖的(bold,impudent)"},{"type":"text","text":"[drfarant]"},{"type":"text","text":"图adefiant teenager一个具有反叛性格的少年"},{"type":"entry","text":"explanatory","headword":"explanatory"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 说明的，解释的(serving to explain)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rk'splaenat:ri]"},{"type":"entry","text":"undirected","headword":"undirected"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 未受指导的(not planned or guided)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Andr'rektrd]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：un（不）+direct（指导）+ed→未受指导的"},{"type":"entry","text":"stash","headword":"stash"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 藏匿(to store in a usually secret place for future use)"},{"type":"text","text":"[stae"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：st（看作stay，待）+ash（灰）→待在灰里→藏匿"},{"type":"entry","text":"undisturbed","headword":"undisturbed"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.未受干扰的，安静的（not disturbed;calm)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Andr'st3:rbd]"},{"type":"text","text":"unmolested"}]},{"number":340,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 30 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"grind","headword":"grind"},{"type":"definition"